","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke w Helios na Scenie","link":null,"screeningId":"063d9706-4e73-4ba2-b9d1-a4505a9135e0","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T13:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T14:46:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-14T13:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-14T12:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":175,"audience":1,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":2868677,"items":[{"movieId":"4c6e0734-8000-45cf-9abe-161ae1a5ff6e","moviePrintId":"d882e05d-f8ef-4987-ba35-fb379d34fca7","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T13:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T14:46:00+02:00","movieName":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":6,"symbol":"HELIOS NA SCENIE","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"d7bb09f1-a1ea-4982-915d-db91d91397cc","duration":176,"description":"Nigdy nie jest za późno, by zacząć od nowa. Emanujący optymizmem i pogodą ducha portret dojrzałej kobiety, która robi wszystko, by ocalić swój dom i siebie.\n\n María Ángeles od 40 lat mieszka w słonecznym apartamencie w marokańskim Tangerze. Gdy zostaje zmuszona do jego opuszczenia, nie potrafi się z tym pogodzić. To, co początkowo wydaje się bolesną koniecznością, nieoczekiwanie staje się jednak nowym początkiem. W życiu Marii Ángeles pojawia się miejsce zarówno na nowych przyjaciół, jak i na niespodziewaną miłość. „Drugie życie” to zdobywca nagrody publiczności festiwalu w Wenecji. W roli głównej zachwycająca Carmen Maura, ikona filmów Almodóvara.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"4a3d74ad-af64-4a6a-a640-e75c762899c8","name":"romans","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/8xyTxjwUwfQ"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/drugiezycieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Drugie życie - Kino Kobiet","link":null,"screeningId":"73cec84a-b9ca-4095-8b58-367f7880d24b","screenId":"26c9e7f7-a631-4826-a86b-552348b7c220","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:56:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T18:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T17:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":217,"audience":180,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":835356,"items":[{"movieId":"efba3b90-d2db-4d41-b474-60d596a59302","moviePrintId":"4a18ef08-42c9-481a-b3ba-e757ea39fec5","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:56:00+02:00","movieName":"Drugie życie","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"26c9e7f7-a631-4826-a86b-552348b7c220","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":2,"symbol":"KINO KOBIET","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"ed834156-8c3f-4332-8f23-3c9b0648811c","duration":108,"description":"Makoto jest zwyczajną nastolatką, spędzającą większość czasu z przyjaciółmi. Kiedy pewnego dnia, spiesząc się z wizytą do ciotki, cudem unika potrącenia przez pociąg – przeskakuje w czasie do momentu sprzed wypadku. Korzystając z nowo poznanych zdolności, naprawia swoje codzienne błędy – od słabych ocen na sprawdzianach po nieudane wyznania miłości. Kiedy jednak dosięgają ją konsekwencje manipulowania czasem, Makoto musi zrobić wszystko, żeby uniknąć straszliwej przyszłości, której nie da się cofnąć.\nOdkryj na nowo film nominowanego do Oscara reżysera Mamoru Hosoda „O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas” na wielkim ekranie, odnowiony w oszałamiającej jakości 4K.\nWIDZOWIE POKAZÓW W RAMACH PROJEKTU HELIOS ANIME OTRZYMAJĄ ","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"ecd4a997-2c14-4fd9-98c2-53ac7087a9bc","name":"anime","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Dziewczynaskaczacaplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Odziewczynieskaczacejprzezczas1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"13","value":"13","description":"od lat 13"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas w Helios Anime","link":null,"screeningId":"9aa34b08-e0a7-43cb-b5df-bba9669ccd8b","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T17:18:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-13T16:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-13T14:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":175,"audience":34,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":54245687,"items":[{"movieId":"9119aa2a-c2cf-4c37-bb76-918faec77850","moviePrintId":"d8e8e674-b775-49f5-8bf8-f210118ecf7d","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T17:18:00+02:00","movieName":"O dziewczynie skaczącej przez czas","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":13,"symbol":"HELIOS ANIME","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"0558005a-3851-48a5-be9d-4ae12a240224","duration":150,"description":"Już 4 czerwca kultowy „Podziemny krąg” („Fight Club”) wraca do kin po ponad 25 latach od premiery!\n\nTen prowokacyjny dramat, z udziałem Brada Pitta i Edwarda Nortona, w reżyserii Davida Finchera, opowiada o znudzonym i wyobcowanym mężczyźnie, który wraz z charyzmatycznym towarzyszem tworzą działający w podziemiu klub walki.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"939b8bbb-4f8f-4fd6-875d-16e483eccdea","name":"thriller","description":""},{"id":"41200b53-4f1a-43c3-9c8e-cbe84751b892","name":"kryminał","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pozdziemnykragplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Podziemnykrag3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Podziemnykrag2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Podziemnykrag1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Podziemny krąg w Helios RePlay","link":null,"screeningId":"6988323d-7f69-4ff5-926c-1f850dbacbee","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-08T20:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-08T23:00:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-08T21:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-08T19:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":102,"audience":6,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":29686786,"items":[{"movieId":"b233f278-496b-4504-ac06-725630c68db1","moviePrintId":"2076a1e7-fffb-4dc7-b499-8398284b48eb","timeFrom":"2026-06-08T20:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-08T23:00:00+02:00","movieName":"Podziemny krąg","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":16,"symbol":"HELIOS REPLAY","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"6c94cbc9-7a80-4a09-b3ad-5602eb24acbd","duration":195,"description":"Obejmująca 34 miasta i 85 koncertów trasa stała się największym tournée w historii koreańskiego artysty. Dodatkowego znaczenia temu wydarzeniu nadaje data koncertu - 13 czerwca, czyli rocznica debiutu BTS - symboliczny moment celebrujący zarówno dotychczasową drogę zespołu, jak i nowy rozdział ich kariery. \n\nTrasa ARIRANG towarzyszy piątemu albumowi studyjnemu grupy i opowiada o tożsamości BTS poprzez szczere emocje, tęsknotę i miłość, które od lat łączą ich z fanami na całym świecie. Imponująca scena 360 stopni sprawia, że widzowie stają się częścią widowiska i mogą poczuć energię koncertu z każdej perspektywy. \n\nNie przegap tego wyjątkowego wydarzenia. Przeżyj wielki powrót BTS na kinowym ekranie 13 czerwca - prosto z Busanu. \n\nUwaga: w wybranych krajach transmisja może odbywać się z opóźnieniem ze względu na różnice stref czasowych.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"249045c8-3c6f-4ffe-abf3-ec3a85a2b1b1","name":"koncert ","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/BTSBusanPlakat(1).jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/BTSczerwiec7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/BTSczerwiec3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/BTSczerwiec2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/BTSczerwiec1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"40","value":"10 lat","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/ORG","name":"BTS World Tour ‘ARIRANG’ in Busan: Live Viewing w Helios na Scenie","link":null,"screeningId":"5b3535e1-65dd-4ff5-b96d-96451f678649","screenId":"26c9e7f7-a631-4826-a86b-552348b7c220","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T18:45:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-13T16:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-13T14:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":217,"audience":22,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":98745545,"items":[{"movieId":"fa55f94f-5ef2-4c03-95c9-d42bd7222047","moviePrintId":"b89ae438-86b6-42da-ab24-2a8f0b940215","timeFrom":"2026-06-13T15:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-13T18:45:00+02:00","movieName":"BTS World Tour ‘ARIRANG’ in Busan: Live Viewing","speakingType":"ORG","printType":"2D","screenId":"26c9e7f7-a631-4826-a86b-552348b7c220","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":6,"symbol":"HELIOS NA SCENIE","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"4f103d1e-9983-4753-a14c-5ad571688313","duration":106,"description":"Bo właśnie tak tak tak się wyżej wznieś! W kinach tylko 10-18 czerwca! Domknij Honmoon i zaśpiewaj najlepsze hity z filmu „K-popowe łowczynie demonów” razem z HUNTR/X i Saja Boys. Pełna wersja karaoke hitowego filmu Netflixa w kinach tylko 10-18 czerwca.\n\nGwiazdy K-popu Rumi, Mira i Zoey w przerwach między koncertami na pełnych stadionach bronią fanów przed nadnaturalnymi zagrożeniami, korzystając ze swoich tajemnych mocy.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"9212e3f5-252f-4d08-b375-2923037a4591","name":"animowany","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/loBwcgZt_m4"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/KPopoweLowczynieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow8.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Kpopowelowczyniedemonow1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke w Helios na Scenie","link":null,"screeningId":"d120acb3-ee54-4784-aac8-15925d2389f9","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T16:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T18:16:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T17:00:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T15:30:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":102,"audience":2,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":2868677,"items":[{"movieId":"4c6e0734-8000-45cf-9abe-161ae1a5ff6e","moviePrintId":"d882e05d-f8ef-4987-ba35-fb379d34fca7","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T16:30:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T18:16:00+02:00","movieName":"K-popowe Łowczynie Demonów: Karaoke","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":6,"symbol":"HELIOS NA SCENIE","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"15358c8a-a67c-4975-b8ba-62e43a97f3f6","duration":108,"description":"Bracia Omul i Mikro wraz z psem Telą opuszczają swoje nadmorskie miasteczko i ruszają w nieznane. Cel ich misji jest jasny – uratować duszę ich siostry, Kimi, którą przejęła Sadumea – legendarny postrach mórz. Aby uratować Kimi, chłopaki muszą uzbroić się w empatię względem napotkanych stworzeń… i siebie samych. Tylko tak uda im się zakopać topór wojenny!","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"9212e3f5-252f-4d08-b375-2923037a4591","name":"animowany","description":""},{"id":"6bcd8fba-fbc2-466a-9f37-ce7a42443c2e","name":"familijny","description":""}],"trailers":[],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/ChlopiecNaKrancachSwiataPLAKAT(1).jpg"],"pictures":[],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"6","value":"6","description":"od lat 6"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/DUB","name":"Chłopiec na krańcach świata - KNTJ","link":null,"screeningId":"45c0e829-30af-4946-8945-421d3bb9de6a","screenId":"6bf9f1aa-e321-4ecf-9a8b-e56468fe51e2","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T10:48:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-09T09:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-09T08:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":97,"audience":21,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":752221236,"items":[{"movieId":"e1b31f3e-5046-45d7-b3b6-94173217364b","moviePrintId":"37a21c8d-ab66-48ea-bba2-15cf1f28ecd6","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T10:48:00+02:00","movieName":"Chłopiec na krańcach świata","speakingType":"DUB","printType":"2D","screenId":"6bf9f1aa-e321-4ecf-9a8b-e56468fe51e2","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":8,"symbol":"KINO NA TEMAT JUNIOR","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"16cdc91a-de6c-4116-b0d2-9b802901b5a1","duration":130,"description":"9-letni Wolfgang po nagłej śmierci matki jest zmuszony zamieszkać ze swoim ojcem, z którym wcześniej nie utrzymywał kontaktu. Chłopiec ma wysoki iloraz inteligencji i marzy o wyjeździe do Paryża, żeby zostać najlepszym pianistą na świecie. Jednak największym wyzwaniem będzie dla niego zbudowanie od zera relacji ze swoim rodzicem.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"6bcd8fba-fbc2-466a-9f37-ce7a42443c2e","name":"familijny","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/-L-IqjJmxro"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/plakatniezwyklychlopak.jpg"],"pictures":[],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/DUB","name":"Niezwykły chłopak - KNT","link":null,"screeningId":"538e02a2-d303-45b1-8035-158a161b3b5e","screenId":"7c9c8e12-b903-4b16-bd4f-7e3356b4b269","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T10:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T12:10:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-09T10:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-09T09:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":219,"audience":54,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":74442356,"items":[{"movieId":"b8efb135-e61e-4d76-90e2-5b127bdeeb9a","moviePrintId":"35048f53-3edd-4e6b-aed1-3eaf3bc8ae92","timeFrom":"2026-06-09T10:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-09T12:10:00+02:00","movieName":"Niezwykły chłopak","speakingType":"DUB","printType":"2D","screenId":"7c9c8e12-b903-4b16-bd4f-7e3356b4b269","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":7,"symbol":"KINO NA TEMAT","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"4add03a9-c644-43b3-a734-acef3cfe73e8","duration":139,"description":"George Fahmy (w tej roli Fares Fares) to największa gwiazda egipskiego kina. Zwany jest “faraonem ekranu”. Zwraca na niego uwagę sam prezydent Egiptu Abd al-Fattah as Sisi, który życzy sobie, aby gwiazdor zagrał główną rolę w filmie biograficznym, gloryfikującym prezydenta. Okazuje się, że jest to propozycja nie do odrzucenia – władza szantażem wymusza na aktorze jej przyjęcie.\n\nPoczątkowo, jak przystało na gwiazdę, bohater liczy na to, że będzie miał sporo do powiedzenia, zarówno w sprawie swojej roli, jak i kształtu całego filmu. Szybko jednak zostaje sprowadzony na ziemię. Głównie za sprawą obecnego na planie tajemniczego doktora Manssoura, który sprawuje pieczę nad produkcją i jej odpowiednim, propagandowym tonem. Sytuację dodatkowo komplikuje romans, w jaki Fahmy wdaje się z żoną jednego z wysoko postawionych generałów. To moment, w którym fikcja i rzeczywistość zaczynają się niebezpiecznie przenikać.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"939b8bbb-4f8f-4fd6-875d-16e483eccdea","name":"thriller","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/-DWKk_XNt0E"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/OrlyRepublikiPlakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Orłyrepubliki1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Orły republiki - Kino Konesera","link":null,"screeningId":"0702a3df-085a-453d-a794-a63aea9f7ae7","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-08T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-08T20:19:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-08T18:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-08T17:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":102,"audience":2,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":54668712,"items":[{"movieId":"9fc5d4d9-9c34-4abf-b663-e2ff769a6f15","moviePrintId":"44473cb6-36f2-41c5-aa94-f46b78efb1fd","timeFrom":"2026-06-08T18:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-08T20:19:00+02:00","movieName":"Orły republiki","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":1,"symbol":"KINO KONESERA","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"feee7612-9cd6-4397-a516-db46be76e2c4","duration":159,"description":"W 1939 roku Szpilman jest cenionym pianistą i kompozytorem, który mieszka wraz z rodziną w Warszawie. Kiedy do stolicy wkraczają naziści, życie żydowskiego muzyka zamienia się w koszmar: traci kolejne prawa, trafia do getta, obserwuje dwa powstania i próbuje przetrwać w zniszczonym mieście. Pomaga mu przypadek, łut szczęścia oraz miłość do muzyki.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"b36e63dc-85ea-4670-93db-f785f49c720e","name":"biograficzny","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/KTDhBh_vL_Q"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/pianistaplakat.png"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Pianista1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Pianista w Helios RePlay","link":null,"screeningId":"27f6b007-6daf-42ac-a0a8-a79022cf1972","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T15:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T17:39:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-14T15:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-14T14:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":175,"audience":2,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":128645,"items":[{"movieId":"117e6eec-1144-4b1a-9600-a86530ca8b3a","moviePrintId":"98e18e82-1d60-4df6-ae6e-e9c76a4d486d","timeFrom":"2026-06-14T15:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-14T17:39:00+02:00","movieName":"Pianista","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":16,"symbol":"HELIOS REPLAY","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"d7bb09f1-a1ea-4982-915d-db91d91397cc","duration":176,"description":"Nigdy nie jest za późno, by zacząć od nowa. Emanujący optymizmem i pogodą ducha portret dojrzałej kobiety, która robi wszystko, by ocalić swój dom i siebie.\n\n María Ángeles od 40 lat mieszka w słonecznym apartamencie w marokańskim Tangerze. Gdy zostaje zmuszona do jego opuszczenia, nie potrafi się z tym pogodzić. To, co początkowo wydaje się bolesną koniecznością, nieoczekiwanie staje się jednak nowym początkiem. W życiu Marii Ángeles pojawia się miejsce zarówno na nowych przyjaciół, jak i na niespodziewaną miłość. „Drugie życie” to zdobywca nagrody publiczności festiwalu w Wenecji. W roli głównej zachwycająca Carmen Maura, ikona filmów Almodóvara.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"4a3d74ad-af64-4a6a-a640-e75c762899c8","name":"romans","description":""},{"id":"14c7bb44-6562-4ad9-8d7a-ab747fa73829","name":"dramat","description":""}],"trailers":["https://www.youtube.com/embed/8xyTxjwUwfQ"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/drugiezycieplakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie7.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie6.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie5.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie4.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie3.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie2.jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Drugiezycie1.jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"15","value":"15","description":"od lat 15"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/NAP","name":"Drugie życie - Kino Kobiet","link":null,"screeningId":"aae9402b-bbb5-4d64-a159-eac5bc25428b","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T17:15:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:11:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T17:45:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T16:15:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":175,"audience":42,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":835356,"items":[{"movieId":"efba3b90-d2db-4d41-b474-60d596a59302","moviePrintId":"4a18ef08-42c9-481a-b3ba-e757ea39fec5","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T17:15:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T20:11:00+02:00","movieName":"Drugie życie","speakingType":"Napisy","printType":"2D","screenId":"e99a42cb-c36e-4032-b393-6585b202e353","movieSubPrintLabel":"PS"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specjalne","description":"","tags":[{"orderNo":2,"symbol":"KINO KOBIET","description":""}]}],"restrictedToCardTypeIds":[],"screenFeatures":[]},{"id":"8548c02a-56bf-4df4-8085-fbb356648e06","duration":110,"description":"Waldek ma dość – w domu chaos, w sieci drama, a jego gamingowy team się sypie. W emocjach robi coś głupiego – pisze złośliwy komentarz… i nieświadomie uruchamia lawinę hejtu, która uderza w jedną z najbliższych mu osób – Delfinę.","ageLongDescription":null,"releaseDate":null,"distributor":null,"distributorId":null,"genres":[{"id":"6bcd8fba-fbc2-466a-9f37-ce7a42443c2e","name":"familijny","description":""},{"id":"726b5445-9bb2-48ff-8ef1-c4e96bb92399","name":"przygodowy","description":""}],"trailers":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/tPGupILl22k"],"posters":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/zaduzynabajki3plakat.jpg"],"pictures":["https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki36(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki35(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki34(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki33(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki32(1).jpg","https://movies.helios.pl/images/Zaduzynabajki31(1).jpg"],"posPosters":[],"banners":[],"ratings":[{"cinemaGroupId":null,"symbol":"10","value":"10","description":"od lat 10"}],"brightcoveVideos":[],"release":"2D/ORG","name":"Za duży na bajki 3 - KNT","link":null,"screeningId":"28ff8e51-9ea3-4e75-bcb6-01eef8092b72","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","cinemaId":"60cfe883-55aa-4e28-be7f-233f589a34cb","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T10:50:00+02:00","saleTimeTo":"2026-06-10T09:30:00+02:00","reservationTimeTo":"2026-06-10T08:00:00+02:00","availabilityStatus":1,"maxOccupancy":102,"audience":50,"generalAdmission":false,"isScreenSwapping":false,"externalId":78676543,"items":[{"movieId":"acb949c5-ada7-4587-a2f9-7c68d2bff707","moviePrintId":"a3db7111-7698-438f-8fdd-6aebf029fa81","timeFrom":"2026-06-10T09:00:00+02:00","timeTo":"2026-06-10T10:50:00+02:00","movieName":"Za duży na bajki 3","speakingType":"ORG","printType":"2D","screenId":"760b0fe0-54ff-4723-bbe0-3f355c7b39f9","movieSubPrintLabel":"ps"}],"tagGroups":[{"symbol":"Projekty Specj